title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update X - USA - released
description:
The latest World Update for MSFS has just been released: World Update X. This time Asobo went back to the USA to optimize the content for this part of the world. The good news is that besides the content several discovery flights, landing challenges and bush trips have been added which you can use to enjoy the updated content.
